417
00:21:03,899 --> 00:21:06,699
I know that man.

418
00:21:06,699 --> 00:21:08,699
He lives in the same condo as me.

419
00:21:08,699 --> 00:21:10,299
Well, we're just about to go over

420
00:21:10,299 --> 00:21:12,299
to your place to play.

