444
00:22:13,299 --> 00:22:14,599
What?

445
00:22:14,599 --> 00:22:16,399
What kind of guy was he?

446
00:22:16,399 --> 00:22:17,999
Did you see his face?

447
00:22:17,999 --> 00:22:20,099
No. I couldn't because it was covered

